---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const locale = 'en' as const;
---
<BaseLayout
  locale={locale}
  title="Privacy — Casa & Studio Indigo"
  description="How the Casa & Studio Indigo website handles contact-form submissions."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-20 prose prose-neutral">
    <h1 class="font-serif">Privacy</h1>
    <p><em>Placeholder — to be finalised before launch.</em></p>
    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>When you send an enquiry, we receive the name, email, phone number (if provided) and message you enter in the form. The form is delivered by Formspree and forwarded to our email.</p>
    <h2>How we use it</h2>
    <p>We use your details only to reply to your enquiry. We do not share them with third parties beyond the delivery service (Formspree) and our email provider.</p>
    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>Under the GDPR you can ask us at any time to access, correct or delete the information you have sent us. Contact us by email or WhatsApp to do so.</p>
    <h2>Cookies &amp; analytics</h2>
    <p>This site uses no analytics and sets no cookies.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
